# Empty sentinel file. See tools/check_gd_scripts_headless.ps1 header.
# Marks the `tests_support/` tree as a vendored / GUT-extending area whose
# `.gd` files (currently the shared bases under `bases/`) cannot parse
# standalone — they `extends GutTest` (or similar) and require GUT's
# class_name registry to be loaded by Godot. Headless GUT runs from the
# dedicated coverage hosts under `tests/godot/*` validate them indirectly.
#
# Note: GUT itself is no longer vendored under this directory; it lives as
# a git submodule at `third_party/Gut/`. Submodule contents are not listed
# by `git ls-files` from the superproject, so the validator skips them
# automatically without needing a sentinel.
